msgid "1. <b>性能对账：</b>数据每 10 分钟写库。若觉延迟，按 <code>Ctrl + F5</code> 强制对账。白名单用户豁免所有拦截。"
msgstr "1. <b>Performance:</b> Data writes every 10 min. Use <code>Ctrl+F5</code> to force sync. Whitelisted users are exempt."

msgid "2. <b>入口保护：</b>系统已自动封锁 wp-login.php 和 wp-admin 目录。请使用 <code>[sba_login_box]</code> 短代码在前台展示登录面板。"
msgstr "2. <b>Entrance:</b> wp-login and wp-admin are blocked. Use <code>[sba_login_box]</code> shortcode for front-end login."

msgid "3. <b>IP 信任：</b>看仪表盘 IP。若为 127.0.0.1 或内网 IP，请根据 CDN/代理环境切换至「Nginx」或「Cloudflare」。"
msgstr "3. <b>IP Trust:</b> Check Dashboard IP. If 127.0.0.1, switch source to Nginx or Cloudflare according to your environment."

msgid "4. <b>AJAX 补丁：</b>无痕访问首页。若「访客轨迹」未增加记录，说明 PHP 被静态缓存截断，此时必须开启。"
msgstr "4. <b>AJAX Patch:</b> If tracks aren't recording due to static caching, enable this feature."

msgid "5. <b>爬虫防御：</b>「Cookie 校验」识别无状态脚本。内置「蜜罐陷阱」会自动诱捕并封禁扫描页面的恶意爬虫。"
msgstr "5. <b>Anti-Bot:</b> Cookie check identifies scripts. Honeypot traps and blocks malicious scanners automatically."

